<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EuroAfricaLink | Procurement & Shipping from Europe to Africa</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Procurement, sourcing and shipping of machinery, parts, automobiles and industrial goods from Europe to Douala, Cameroon and beyond." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="EuroAfricaLink | Procurement & Shipping from Europe to Africa" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="We source machinery, vehicles, parts and merchandise in Europe, manage the purchase and arrange shipping to Douala and other destinations." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://api.fontshare.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=satoshi@400,500,700&f[]=boska@400,500,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root, [data-theme="light"] {
      --font-display: 'Boska', Georgia, serif;
      --font-body: 'Satoshi', Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      --text-xs: clamp(0.75rem, 0.7rem + 0.25vw, 0.875rem);
      --text-sm: clamp(0.875rem, 0.8rem + 0.35vw, 1rem);
      --text-base: clamp(1rem, 0.95rem + 0.25vw, 1.125rem);
      --text-lg: clamp(1.125rem, 1rem + 0.75vw, 1.5rem);
      --text-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1.25vw, 2.25rem);
      --text-2xl: clamp(2rem, 1.2rem + 2.5vw, 3.8rem);
      --space-1: 0.25rem;
      --space-2: 0.5rem;
      --space-3: 0.75rem;
      --space-4: 1rem;
      --space-5: 1.25rem;
      --space-6: 1.5rem;
      --space-8: 2rem;
      --space-10: 2.5rem;
      --space-12: 3rem;
      --space-16: 4rem;
      --space-20: 5rem;
      --space-24: 6rem;
      --color-bg: #f7f6f2;
      --color-surface: #fbfaf7;
      --color-surface-2: #f1eee7;
      --color-border: rgba(40, 37, 29, 0.12);
      --color-text: #28251d;
      --color-text-muted: #6f6d67;
      --color-text-inverse: #f9f8f4;
      --color-primary: #01696f;
      --color-primary-hover: #0c4e54;
      --color-accent: #d19900;
      --color-accent-soft: rgba(209, 153, 0, 0.12);
      --radius-sm: 0.5rem;
      --radius-md: 0.9rem;
      --radius-lg: 1.25rem;
      --radius-xl: 1.75rem;
      --radius-full: 999px;
      --shadow-sm: 0 6px 18px rgba(31, 25, 18, 0.06);
      --shadow-md: 0 18px 45px rgba(31, 25, 18, 0.09);
      --content: 1180px;
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --color-bg: #181715;
      --color-surface: #201f1d;
      --color-surface-2: #2b2927;
      --color-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --color-text: #ede9df;
      --color-text-muted: #b6b1a8;
      --color-text-inverse: #151412;
      --color-primary: #54a0aa;
      --color-primary-hover: #73b4bc;
      --color-accent: #e7b342;
      --color-accent-soft: rgba(231, 179, 66, 0.13);
      --shadow-sm: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      --shadow-md: 0 18px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }

    * , *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--color-text);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, var(--color-accent-soft), transparent 22%), var(--color-bg);
    }
    img, svg { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button, input, select, textarea { font: inherit; }
    .skip-link {
      position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: -3rem; background: var(--color-primary); color: white;
      padding: .6rem .9rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); z-index: 1000;
    }
    .skip-link:focus { top: 1rem; }
    .container { width: min(var(--content), calc(100% - 2rem)); margin: 0 auto; }
    .site-header {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50; backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 82%, transparent);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .nav {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--space-4);
      min-height: 78px;
    }
    .brand {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .01em;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 14px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 55%, black));
      color: white; display: grid; place-items: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .brand-text strong { display: block; font-size: var(--text-sm); }
    .brand-text span { display: block; font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
    .nav-links a { padding: .55rem .7rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); }
    .nav-links a:hover { background: var(--color-surface-2); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; gap: .75rem; align-items: center; }
    .theme-toggle, .menu-toggle {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      background: var(--color-surface); color: var(--color-text); display: grid; place-items: center; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .menu-toggle { display: none; }
    .button {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: .55rem;
      min-height: 46px; padding: .8rem 1.2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); font-size: var(--text-sm);
      font-weight: 700; border: 1px solid transparent; transition: .18s ease;
    }
    .button-primary { background: var(--color-primary); color: white; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
    .button-primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-hover); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .button-secondary { background: transparent; border-color: var(--color-border); }
    .button-secondary:hover { background: var(--color-surface); }

    .hero {
      padding: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 7rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.12fr .88fr; gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); align-items: center;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .55rem; padding: .45rem .85rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-xs);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .09em;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      margin: 1rem 0 1rem; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 500; line-height: .98; font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      max-width: 12ch;
    }
    .hero p {
      max-width: 60ch; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .8rem; margin-bottom: 1.35rem; }
    .hero-points {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: .9rem; margin-top: 1.4rem;
    }
    .hero-point {
      padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: var(--color-surface); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }
    .hero-point strong { display: block; margin-bottom: .2rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); }
    .hero-point span { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .hero-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-surface), color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 60%, var(--color-surface-2)));
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-panel-top {
      padding: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-panel-top .tag { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; }
    .hero-visual {
      padding: 1.4rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .route-card, .quote-card {
      background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: calc(var(--radius-xl) - .6rem); padding: 1rem;
    }
    .route-line { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .75rem; justify-content: space-between; font-size: var(--text-sm); }
    .route-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(1,105,111,.12); }
    .route-dash { flex: 1; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent)); opacity: .7; }
    .mini-list { display: grid; gap: .75rem; }
    .mini-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: .7rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .mini-item b { color: var(--color-text); display: block; }

    section { padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem) 0; }
    .section-heading { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .section-heading h2 {
      margin: 0; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }
    .section-heading p { margin: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 58ch; }

    .services-grid, .audience-grid, .faq-grid { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); }
    .audience-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); }
    .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); }

    .card {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.2rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .card .kicker {
      font-size: var(--text-xs); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: .55rem;
    }
    .card h3 { margin: 0 0 .45rem; font-size: var(--text-lg); line-height: 1.15; }
    .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }
    .card ul { margin: .85rem 0 0; padding-left: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }

    .process {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 1rem;
    }
    .step {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.15rem;
    }
    .step-no { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-primary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; margin-bottom: .45rem; }
    .step h3 { margin: 0 0 .35rem; font-size: var(--text-base); }
    .step p { margin: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }

    .language-wrap {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 1rem;
    }
    .lang-card { padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); }
    .lang-card h3 { margin: 0 0 .55rem; font-size: var(--text-lg); }
    .lang-card p, .lang-card li { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }
    .lang-card ul { padding-left: 1rem; margin: .8rem 0 0; }
    .sample-box {
      margin-top: 1rem; background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px dashed var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 1rem;
    }
    .sample-box strong { display: block; margin-bottom: .4rem; color: var(--color-text); }

    .contact-wrap {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; gap: 1rem;
    }
    form {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: 1.2rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .field-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: .9rem; }
    .field { display: grid; gap: .35rem; margin-bottom: .9rem; }
    .field label { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; }
    .field input, .field select, .field textarea {
      width: 100%; min-height: 48px; padding: .85rem .95rem; border-radius: .95rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-text);
    }
    .field textarea { min-height: 136px; resize: vertical; }
    .contact-info {
      display: grid; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .info-panel {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: 1.2rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .info-panel h3 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: .5rem; font-size: var(--text-lg); }
    .info-panel p, .info-panel li { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .info-panel ul { padding-left: 1rem; margin: .75rem 0 0; }

    .site-footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 1.4rem 0 2.2rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
    .footer-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero, .contact-wrap, .language-wrap, .services-grid, .faq-grid, .process, .audience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero h1 { max-width: 14ch; }
      .nav-links { display: none; position: absolute; top: 78px; left: 1rem; right: 1rem; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: .8rem; flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .menu-toggle { display: grid; }
      .field-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container { width: min(var(--content), calc(100% - 1rem)); }
      .nav { min-height: 72px; }
      .hero-points { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-actions .button { display: none; }
      .hero { padding-top: 2.2rem; }
      .section-heading { align-items: start; flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="EuroAfricaLink home">
        <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M4 16L9 11L13 15L20 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M15 8H20V13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="brand-text">
          <strong>EuroAfricaLink</strong>
          <span>Sourcing • Procurement • Shipping</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links" id="navMenu" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#process">How it works</a>
        <a href="#french">French version</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="nav-actions">
        <button class="theme-toggle" type="button" data-theme-toggle aria-label="Switch theme">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"></path></svg>
        </button>
        <button class="menu-toggle" type="button" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Open menu">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18"/></svg>
        </button>
        <a href="#contact" class="button button-primary">Request a quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero" id="top">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Based in Douala, Cameroon</span>
          <h1>We source in Europe, purchase on your behalf, and ship to your destination.</h1>
          <p>
            For companies and individuals buying machinery, spare parts, automobiles and merchandise from Europe,
            we coordinate sourcing, supplier checks, purchasing and transport to Douala and other African destinations.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="#contact">Start a request</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="#french">Voir la version française</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-points">
            <div class="hero-point"><strong>Trusted sourcing</strong><span>Machinery, vehicles, industrial parts and commercial goods.</span></div>
            <div class="hero-point"><strong>One contact</strong><span>From supplier search to export and shipping coordination.</span></div>
            <div class="hero-point"><strong>Clear process</strong><span>Request, quote, approval, purchase, shipment, delivery follow-up.</span></div>
            <div class="hero-point"><strong>Douala-focused</strong><span>Built for importers in Cameroon and the wider region.</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero-card" aria-label="Service overview">
          <div class="hero-panel-top">
            <div>
              <div class="tag">Typical route</div>
              <strong>Europe to Douala</strong>
            </div>
            <span class="eyebrow" style="margin:0;">Sea • Air • Road</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-visual">
            <div class="route-card">
              <div class="route-line">
                <span>Supplier in Europe</span>
                <span class="route-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="route-dash" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span>Douala / Destination</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="quote-card mini-list">
              <div class="mini-item">
                <span>01</span>
                <div><b>Tell us what you need</b>Brand, model, quantity, budget and deadline.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-item">
                <span>02</span>
                <div><b>Receive matched offers</b>We compare suppliers, product details and shipment options.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-item">
                <span>03</span>
                <div><b>Approve and ship</b>We handle purchase coordination and transport arrangements.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section id="services">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <h2>Services</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Use this site as a professional front door for sourcing enquiries from importers, traders, SMEs and individual buyers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="kicker">Procurement</div>
            <h3>Machinery and equipment sourcing</h3>
            <p>We find construction, industrial and agricultural equipment from reliable European suppliers based on your exact requirements.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="kicker">Automotive</div>
            <h3>Cars, trucks and commercial vehicles</h3>
            <p>We help clients purchase new or used automobiles, fleet vehicles and utility units with documented options before commitment.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="kicker">Parts</div>
            <h3>Spare parts and mixed merchandise</h3>
            <p>We source OEM and aftermarket parts, tools and smaller goods, then consolidate them for efficient shipment.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <h2>Who this is for</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Keep the message practical and commercial so visitors immediately understand whether your service fits their needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="kicker">Businesses</div>
            <h3>SMEs, contractors and import companies</h3>
            <p>Ideal for businesses that need dependable sourcing support, recurring supply, purchase coordination and organized shipping.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Construction and industrial buyers</li>
              <li>Auto dealers and fleet operators</li>
              <li>Import and trading companies</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="kicker">Individuals</div>
            <h3>Private buyers with a clear brief</h3>
            <p>Also suitable for individual clients purchasing one vehicle, one machine or a specific set of parts from Europe.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Single-unit vehicle purchase</li>
              <li>Targeted spare part orders</li>
              <li>Personal import assistance</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="process">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <h2>How it works</h2>
          </div>
          <p>A clear service flow builds trust and reduces back-and-forth with new clients.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process">
          <article class="step">
            <div class="step-no">Step 1</div>
            <h3>Client request</h3>
            <p>The buyer shares the product description, target budget, quantity and destination.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="step-no">Step 2</div>
            <h3>Sourcing and quotation</h3>
            <p>We identify suitable European suppliers and present pricing, specifications and shipment options.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="step-no">Step 3</div>
            <h3>Approval and purchase</h3>
            <p>Once the client approves, we coordinate the purchase process and required documentation.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="step-no">Step 4</div>
            <h3>Shipping and follow-up</h3>
            <p>We arrange the best available transport method and support delivery follow-up to destination.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="french">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <h2>French version</h2>
          </div>
          <p>This section gives you ready-to-use French web text for the same business, which is especially useful for Cameroon-based clients.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="language-wrap">
          <article class="lang-card">
            <h3>Texte d’accueil</h3>
            <p>
              Nous accompagnons les entreprises et les particuliers qui souhaitent acheter des machines,
              des pièces détachées, des automobiles et diverses marchandises en Europe. Nous recherchons,
              vérifions, achetons et organisons l’expédition vers Douala et toute autre destination convenue.
            </p>
            <div class="sample-box">
              <strong>Titre principal</strong>
              Approvisionnement et expédition de l’Europe vers l’Afrique.
            </div>
            <div class="sample-box">
              <strong>Sous-titre</strong>
              Un interlocuteur unique pour la recherche de fournisseurs, l’achat et l’organisation du transport.
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="lang-card">
